= Dissent Within the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span>

Despite [+ nsdap_leader +] forcing <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> commander Wilhelm Stegmann to sign a statement of submission, the renegade has bolted once again. Proclaiming defiance against his state gauleiter, he’s formed an independent paramilitary group—taking some 7,000 loyal <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> men with him. [+ nsdap_leader +] retaliated by expelling him outright from the party.

In past cases, condemnation from [+ nsdap_leader +] was enough to snuff out dissent. But this time, Stegmann defied the ban and retained fierce loyalty among his ranks. Local <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazi</span> organizations are now split—forced to choose between backing their gauleiter or Stegmann—crippling their state organization.

